explanation: The solution uses dynamic programming to pre-compute all palindromic substrings and then uses another dynamic programming array to track the maximum number of non-overlapping palindromic substrings of length at least k. The key strength lies in its ability to efficiently pre-compute and store the necessary information, allowing for an optimal solution. 
